{"id":1233,"date":"2024-08-03T21:53:21","date_gmt":"2024-08-03T21:53:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1233"},"modified":"2024-08-13T19:53:22","modified_gmt":"2024-08-13T19:53:22","slug":"mission-037","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-037\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #037: Lost Hanky"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #037: Lost Hanky<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Magnolia Town, Magnolia Cafe &#8211; outside on a Saturday<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete the main story missions up until Magnolia Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Return the Handkerchief to the boy at the Magnolia Cafe<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Lycanium Z<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A rich boy at the Magnolia Cafe has lost his handkerchief. If you return it, he\u2019ll give you a <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/z-crystals\/\">Lycanium Z<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/037\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-magnolia-cafe-on-saturday.jpg\" alt=\"The Magnolia Cafe on Saturday \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Magnolia Cafe on Saturday<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The visitors and features at Magnolia Town\u2019s Magnolia Caf\u00e9 will change depending on the day of the week and the time of day.<\/p>\n<p>Visit the outside tables of the Cafe at any time on Saturday and you\u2019ll find an item.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/037\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-grubby-hanky.jpg\" alt=\"The Grubby Hanky \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Grubby Hanky<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The item is the Grubby Hanky, and you\u2019ll be given a mission to return it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/037\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-mission.jpg\" alt=\"The mission \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mission<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The hanky was dropped by a Friday regular, so you\u2019ll have to go back to the Cafe on the following Friday to return it.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/037\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-owner-of-the-handkerchief.jpg\" alt=\"The owner of the Handkerchief \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The owner of the Handkerchief<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Note:<\/strong> Be aware that modifying the date on your computer to affect the emulator can have unintended effects on the game. If you don\u2019t want to wait all that time to complete the mission, the safest way of doing so is doing it on a real Friday.\n<\/div>\n<p>Alternatively if you want to skip ahead in time, here\u2019s how:<\/p>\n<p>With the game closed, turn the clocks back to the previous Saturday, and pick up the hanky. You will then need to leave Magnolia Town &#8211; go east to Magnolia Fields &#8211; so that the Cafe is reset.<\/p>\n<p>Then close the game again, return the calendar to normal, and because it is a real Friday and the real date, your save will more than likely be fine going forward.<\/p>\n<p>Return to Magnolia Caf\u00e9 on Friday and a rich boy will be sitting at the table the item was on. Give the Grubby Hanky to him, and he\u2019ll give you the Lycanium Z.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1234,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1233","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1233","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1234"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1233"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1233"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}